node.text: Chip and Jo first met Bailey in 2017 when he was undergoing treatment for osteosarcoma. Thanks to St. Jude™, Bailey is now cancer-free, and you can find him playing golf, spending time with his family, or hitting the road (he’s a new driver!). We love @stjude not only because they help kids like Bailey fight cancer and disease, but also because they cover all the costs of a family receiving care, including treatment, housing, meals, and travel. Now that’s a mission we can get behind! Head to @chipgaines account to see him catch up with Bailey. #ChipInForStJude
